== 古生態學 ==
[[Image:Zuchengtyrannus_VS_Sinoceratops.jpg|thumb]]的骨架模型。諸城暴龍是辛格庄組的主要掠食者之一]] 
中國角龍的發現地諸城位於山東的[[膠萊盆地|膠萊盆地]]內，該盆地是由陸相[[沉積岩|沉積岩]]夾雜[[火成岩|火成岩]]組成的[[中生代|中生代]][[沖積平原|沖積平原]]，地層中發現的[[玄武岩|玄武岩]]和[[沉積岩#碎屑沉積岩|碎屑沉積岩]]顯示此地帶在當時曾有過[[火山|火山]]活動。膠萊盆地於白堊紀形成時期是恐龍化石豐富的[[萊陽群|萊陽群]]、[[大盛群|大盛群]]、[[青山群|青山群]]與王氏群地層（四個{{link-en|群 (地質學)|Group (stratigraphy)|群}}的層位依序由下至上，亦即年代相對由早至晚）<ref>{{cite journal | author = 孟繁聪, 李天福, 薛怀民, 刘福来, 许志琴 | title = 胶莱盆地晚白垩世不同地幔源区的两种基性岩浆——诸城玄武岩和胶州玄武岩的对比 | journal = ''Acta Petrologica Sinica''（岩石学报） | volume = 6 | year = 2006 | pages = 1644-1656 | issn = 1000-0569 | url = http://www.ysxb.ac.cn/ysxb/ch/reader/create_pdf.aspx?file_no=200606169 | access-date = 2019-07-21 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20181123201058/http://www.ysxb.ac.cn/ysxb/ch/reader/create_pdf.aspx?file_no=200606169 | archive-date = 2018-11-23 | dead-url = no }}</ref>，而中國角龍化石所在的辛格莊組則為王氏群的四個[[組_(地質學)|組]]中，年代第二早者（即王氏群下部，年代相當於白堊紀晚期）<ref>{{cite journal | author = 李金良, 张岳桥, 柳宗泉, 任凤楼, 袁嘉音 | title = 胶莱盆地沉积-沉降史分析与构造演化 | journal = 中国地质 | volume = 34 | issue = 2 | year = 2007 | pages = 240-250 | issn = 1000-3657 | url = http://geochina.cgs.gov.cn/ch/reader/view_abstract.aspx?file_no=20070205&flag=1 | access-date = 2019-07-21 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20181123200753/http://geochina.cgs.gov.cn/ch/reader/view_abstract.aspx?file_no=20070205&flag=1 | archive-date = 2018-11-23 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>。王氏群整體的定年研究迄今尚未齊全，但一般認為辛格莊組的年代應落在[[森諾曼階|森諾曼階]]<ref name = "Hu2001">{{cite book | author = 胡承志, 程政武, 庞其清, 方晓思 | title = 巨型山东龙 | publisher = 地质出版社 | isbn = 7-116-03472-2 | date = 2001年10月 }}</ref>至[[坎帕階|坎帕階]]<ref>{{ cite journal | author = Hong, J.; Miyata, T. | title = Strike-slip origin of Cretaceous Mazhan Basin, Tan-Lu fault zone, Shandong, east China | journal = ''The Island Arc'' | volume = 8 | year = 1999 | pages = 90–91 | issn = 1440-1738 | doi = 10.1046/j.1440-1738.1999.00226.x }}</ref>之間。

除了中國角龍外，如體型較小的原始角龍類[[諸城角龍|諸城角龍]]<ref>{{cite journal | author = Xu, X.; Wang, K.; Zhao, X.; Sullivan, C.; Chen, S. | title = A New Leptoceratopsid (Ornithischia: Ceratopsia) from the Upper Cretaceous of Shandong, China and Its Implications for Neoceratopsian Evolution | journal = ''[[PLOS_ONE|PLoS ONE]]'' | volume = 5 | issue = 11 | year = 2010 | pages = e13835 | issn = 1932-6203 | doi = 10.1371/journal.pone.0013835 | pmc = 2973951 | pmid = 21079798 | url = https://journals.plos.org/plosone/article?id=10.1371/journal.pone.0013835 | access-date = 2019-07-21 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190629102119/https://journals.plos.org/plosone/article?id=10.1371%2Fjournal.pone.0013835 | archive-date = 2019-06-29 | dead-url = no }}</ref>、大型[[鴨嘴龍類|鴨嘴龍類]][[山東龍|山東龍]]<ref>{{ cite journal | author = 胡承志 | title = 山东诸城巨型鸭嘴龙化石 | journal = 地质学报 | volume = 2 | year = 1973 | pages = 179-206 | issn = 0001-5717 }}</ref>（屬於巨型鴨嘴龍類的[[巨大華夏龍|華夏龍]]<ref>{{cite journal | author = 赵喜进, 王克柏, 李敦景 | title = 巨大华夏龙 | journal = 地质通报 | volume = 30 | issue = 11 | year = 2011 | pages = 240-250 | issn = 1671-1688 | url = http://dzhtb.cgs.cn/ch/reader/create_pdf.aspx?file_no=20111103&flag=1&year_id=2011&quarter_id=11 | access-date = 2018-11-23 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20181123200753/http://dzhtb.cgs.cn/ch/reader/create_pdf.aspx?file_no=20111103&flag=1&year_id=2011&quarter_id=11 | archive-date = 2018-11-23 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>和[[諸城龍|諸城龍]]<ref>{{ cite journal | author = 赵喜进, 李敦景, 韩岗, 赵华锡, 刘凤光, 李来进, 方晓思 | title = 山东的巨大诸城龙 | journal = 地球学报 | volume = 28 | issue = 2 | year = 2007 | pages = 111-122 | issn = 1006-3021 | url = }}</ref>可能亦為其[[異名|異名]]）等草食恐龍也發現於辛格庄組地層；屬於大型[[暴龍類|暴龍類]]的[[諸城暴龍|諸城暴龍]]也生活於此時期的該地<ref>{{ cite journal | author = Hone, D. W. E.; Wang, K.; Sullivan, C.; Zhao, X.; Chen, S.; Li, D.; Ji, S.; Ji, Q.; Xu, X. | title = A new, large tyrannosaurine theropod from the Upper Cretaceous of China | journal = ''Cretaceous Research'' | volume = 32 | issue = 4 | year = 2011 | pages = 495–503 | issn = 0195-6671 | doi = 10.1016/j.cretres.2011.03.005 }}</ref>，且可能將中國角龍作為獵食對象之一。而[[美國|美國]]古生物學家{{link-en|葛瑞格利·保羅|Gregory S. Paul}}推論，中國角龍亦可能和生存年代比辛格莊組更晚的動物共存，如[[將軍頂組|將軍頂組]]的[[譚氏龍|譚氏龍]]，以及[[金崗口組|金崗口組]]（有些地質學家會將其併入[[紅土崖組|紅土崖組]]<ref>{{ cite journal | author = 閆峻, 陳江峰 | title = 胶州大西庄晚中生代玄武岩中单斜辉石巨晶 | journal = 安徽理工大学学报（自然科学版） | volume = 25 | issue = 3 | year = 2005 | pages = 9–13 | issn = 1671-7872 }}</ref><ref>{{ cite journal | author = Li, Y.; He, H.; Deng, C.; Pan, Y.; Ji, Q.; Wang, C.; Zheng, D.; Zhu, R. | title = <sup>40</sup>Ar/<sup>39</sup>Ar dating results from the Shijiatun Formation, Jiaolai Basin: New age constraints on the Cretaceous terrestrial volcanic-sedimentary sequence of China | journal = ''Anais da Cretaceous Research'' | volume = 86 | year = 2018 | pages = | issn = 0195-6671 | doi = 10.1016/j.cretres.2018.03.003 | url = }}</ref>）的[[青島龍|青島龍]]等等<ref name=Paul2016/><ref name = "Hu2001"/>。

== 古生物地理學 ==
[[Image:Ceratopsian_map.png|thumb]]已知化石的分布，顯示角龍科（藍點）幾乎都分布於北美洲。圖中日本[[九州_(日本)|九州]]的紀錄是一顆可能屬於角龍科的不完整牙齒<ref>{{cite journal | author = Manabe, M.; Tsuihiji, T.; Miyake, Y.; Komatsu, T. | title = A possible ceratopsid tooth from the Upper Cretaceous of Kyushu, Japan | journal = ''Bulletin of National Museum of Nature and Science Series C'' | volume = 42 | year = 2016 | pages = 29–34 | issn = 0385-244X | url = https://www.kahaku.go.jp/research/publication/geology/download/42/BNMNS_C42_29-34.pdf | access-date = 2019-07-21 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190717150816/https://www.kahaku.go.jp/research/publication/geology/download/42/BNMNS_C42_29-34.pdf | archive-date = 2019-07-17 | dead-url = no }}</ref>]] 
1970年代伊始，陸續有化石紀錄顯示，許多白堊紀晚期的恐龍類群，如[[暴龍類|暴龍類]]<ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.livescience.com/53877-t-rex-was-invasive-species.html | title = T. Rex Was Likely an Invasive Species | date = 2016-02-29 | author = Geggel, Laura | publisher = Live Science | access-date = 2019-07-21 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190714170020/https://www.livescience.com/53877-t-rex-was-invasive-species.html | archive-date = 2019-07-14 | dead-url = no }}</ref>、[[馳龍類|馳龍類]]<ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.deseretnews.com/article/577984/NM-dinosaur-discoveries-make-paleontologists-bliss-extinct.html | title = N.M. dinosaur discoveries make paleontologists' bliss extinct | date = 1997-08-19 | author = [[Associated_Press|Associated Press]] | publisher = Deseret News | access-date = 2019-07-21 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190714164521/https://www.deseretnews.com/article/577984/NM-dinosaur-discoveries-make-paleontologists-bliss-extinct.html | archive-date = 2019-07-14 | dead-url = no }}</ref>、[[甲龍類|甲龍類]]<ref>{{cite web | url = http://blogs.discovermagazine.com/d-brief/2018/07/19/25809/ | title = New Species Of Armored Dinosaur Hints At Ancient Migration | date = 2018-07-19 | author = Betz, Eric | publisher = [[發現_(雜誌)|Discover]] | access-date = 2019-07-21 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180927061542/http://blogs.discovermagazine.com/d-brief/2018/07/19/25809/ | archive-date = 2018-09-27 | dead-url = no }}</ref>、[[鴨嘴龍類|鴨嘴龍類]]<ref>{{cite journal | author = Godefroit, P.; Bolotsky, Y.; Alifanov, V. | title = A remarkable hollow-crested hadrosaur from Russia: An Asian origin for lambeosaurines | journal = ''Comptes Rendus Palevol'' | volume = 2 | year = 2003 | pages = 143–151 | issn = 1631-0683 | doi = 10.1016/S1631-0683(03)00017-4 | url = https://www.researchgate.net/publication/40662276_A_remarkable_hollow-crested_hadrosaur_from_Russia_An_Asian_origin_for_lambeosaurines | access-date = 2019-07-14 | archive-date = 2019-09-20 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190920161520/https://www.researchgate.net/publication/40662276_A_remarkable_hollow-crested_hadrosaur_from_Russia_An_Asian_origin_for_lambeosaurines }}</ref>和[[鐮刀龍類|鐮刀龍類]]<ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.ibtimes.com/dinosaurs-used-alaska-superhighway-migration-route-north-america-footprints-suggest-2706315 | title = Dinosaurs Used Alaska As 'Superhighway' Migration Route To North America, Footprints Suggest | date = 2018-08-07 | author = Sharma, Shubham | publisher = [[國際財經時報|International Business Times]] | access-date = 2019-07-21 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190714164519/https://www.ibtimes.com/dinosaurs-used-alaska-superhighway-migration-route-north-america-footprints-suggest-2706315 | archive-date = 2019-07-14 | dead-url = no }}</ref>，在[[亞洲|亞洲]]和[[北美洲|北美洲]]兩地都有分布，且在兩地也都演化出不少[[物種|物種]]。基於數量可觀的化石紀錄，大部分古生物學家都認為在此時期，恐龍能在亞洲和北美洲之間交流和遷徙。美國古生物學家{{link-en|安東尼·費歐利羅|Anthony Fiorillo}}綜合古生物學與[[地質學|地質學]]證據，也指出這條使兩地恐龍得以來往的通道很可能即位於現今的[[俄羅斯|俄羅斯]][[俄羅斯遠東地區|遠東]]和[[阿拉斯加|阿拉斯加]]之間，相當於白堊紀的[[白令陸橋|白令陸橋]]<ref>{{cite journal | author = Fiorillo, A. R. | title = Dinosaurs of Alaska: Implications for the Cretaceous origin of Beringia | journal = ''Special Paper of the Geological Society of America'' | volume = 442 | year = 2008 | pages = 313–326 | issn = 0072-1077 | doi = 10.1130/2008.442(15) | url = https://www.researchgate.net/publication/236585195_Dinosaurs_of_Alaska_Implications_for_the_Cretaceous_origin_of_Beringia | access-date = 2019-07-14 | archive-date = 2020-07-14 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200714062405/https://www.researchgate.net/publication/236585195_Dinosaurs_of_Alaska_Implications_for_the_Cretaceous_origin_of_Beringia }}</ref>。

但作為白堊紀晚期，北半球代表性的植食性動物，角龍科的地理分散程度卻遠遠低於同時期大部分恐龍類群，在[[歐亞大陸|歐亞大陸]]也少有族群分布。更精確的說，在中國角龍被發現以前，所有的角龍科化石都僅見於北美洲西部{{noteTag|1=化石發現於[[烏茲別克|烏茲別克]]的白堊紀晚期角龍類[[圖蘭角龍|圖蘭角龍]]，曾一度被認為屬於角龍科，但徐星等人的分析顯示，圖蘭角龍缺少數個角龍科的[[共有衍徵|共有衍徵]]，因此不能歸類為角龍科成員<ref name = "xu10"/>。}}。徐星等人認為，亞洲的古生物學發展和北美相比較晚{{noteTag|1=以角龍類為例，北美洲早在19世紀中期就發現了第一批角龍類化石，到1920年代亞洲首度發現角龍類時，北美已經發表了18個角龍類的[[屬|屬]]。（詳見{{link-en|角龍類研究歷史|Timeline of ceratopsian research}}）}}，樣本採集不足，或是當時亞洲的自然環境較不適合角龍科恐龍發展{{noteTag|1=角龍科化石通常都埋藏於濕潤的氣候環境，但亞洲的白堊紀晚期恐龍大多都來自當時是乾燥環境的地區<ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.newscientist.com/article/dn16363-dino-graveyard-reveals-first-asian-triceratops/ | title = Dino 'graveyard' reveals first Asian triceratops | author = Hecht, Jeff | publisher = [[New_Scientist|New Scientist]] | date = 2009-01-06 | access-date = 2019-07-21 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190717150824/https://www.newscientist.com/article/dn16363-dino-graveyard-reveals-first-asian-triceratops/ | archive-date = 2019-07-17 | dead-url = no }}</ref>，中國角龍所在的地層也被認為處於乾旱氣候，環境條件相當不利於恐龍生存<ref>{{cite journal | author = 旷红伟, 柳永清, 董超, 彭楠, 许欢, 王宝红, 章朋, 王克柏, 陈树清, 张艳霞 | title = 山东诸城晚白垩世恐龙化石埋藏学研究 | journal = 地质学报 | volume = 88 | issue = 8 | year = 2014 | pages = 1353–1371 | issn = 0001-5717 | url = http://www.igeodata.org/bitstream/20.500.11758/293/1/%E5%B1%B1%E4%B8%9C%E8%AF%B8%E5%9F%8E%E6%99%9A%E7%99%BD%E5%9E%A9%E4%B8%96%E6%81%90%E9%BE%99%E5%8C%96%E7%9F%B3%E5%9F%8B%E8%97%8F%E5%AD%A6%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6.pdf | access-date = 2019-07-17 | archive-date = 2020-07-14 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200714062415/http://www.igeodata.org/bitstream/20.500.11758/293/1/%E5%B1%B1%E4%B8%9C%E8%AF%B8%E5%9F%8E%E6%99%9A%E7%99%BD%E5%9E%A9%E4%B8%96%E6%81%90%E9%BE%99%E5%8C%96%E7%9F%B3%E5%9F%8B%E8%97%8F%E5%AD%A6%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6.pdf }}</ref>。}}，才導致角龍科在亞洲如此罕見<ref name = "xu10"/>。

徐星等人鑑於原始的角龍類多發現於亞洲，且在角龍類演化史中發生過多次由亞洲向北美洲發展的事件，加上中國角龍的發現，因而推論大型角龍也同樣發源於亞洲，後來遷徙至北美洲並發展成新的物種，如同其他同時分布於亞洲與北美的白堊紀恐龍類群<ref name = "xu10"/>。

== 大眾文化 ==
中國角龍在2018年電影《[[侏羅紀世界：殞落國度|侏羅紀世界：殞落國度]]》中數度出現，並與一隻[[食肉牛龍|食肉牛龍]]發生衝突<ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.ibtimes.com.au/jurassic-world-fallen-kingdom-more-dinosaurs-all-previous-movies-combined-1568253 | title = 'Jurassic World: Fallen Kingdom': More dinosaurs than all previous movies combined | author = Trivedi, Sachin | publisher = International Business Times Australia | date = 2018-06-16 | access-date = 2019-07-21 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180713190455/http://www.ibtimes.com.au/jurassic-world-fallen-kingdom-more-dinosaurs-all-previous-movies-combined-1568253 | archive-date = 2018-07-13 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。電影中的中國角龍在頭盾的窩窗（fenestra）上有明顯的空心洞孔，雖然中國角龍頭骨的窩窗確實是空心的，但咸信角龍類的窩窗在活著的時候應該有皮膚覆蓋著<ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.nhm.ac.uk/discover/why-we-love-jurassic-world-fallen-kingdom-even-though-it-is-wrong.html | title = Why we love Jurassic World 2 (even though it's wrong) | author = Button, David | publisher = [[自然史博物館_(倫敦)|Natural History Museum]] | date = 2018-06-22 | access-date = 2019-07-21 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180929234135/http://www.nhm.ac.uk/discover/why-we-love-jurassic-world-fallen-kingdom-even-though-it-is-wrong.html | archive-date = 2018-09-29 | dead-url = no }}</ref><!---（此段無來源佐證），此一特徵應是參考自動畫電影[[與恐龍冒險3D|與恐龍冒險3D]]中的[[厚鼻龍|厚鼻龍]]主角，而官方也設定該物種原本為厚鼻龍，後來才修改為中國角龍--->。作為[[侏羅紀公園系列|侏羅紀公園系列]]電影的第五部作品，此作出現更多諸如中國角龍等較不為大眾熟知的恐龍物種，同時這也是非北美洲出土的角龍類首次出現在[[好萊塢|好萊塢]]作品中。然而忽略電影中的人為因素，就地理分布而言，亞洲大陸上的中國角龍和南美大陸的食肉牛龍在現實中是不可能相遇的。此外，中國角龍也曾出現在該電影與[[非政府組織|非政府]][[環境保護主義|環保]]組織{{link-en|野生救援|WildAid}}合作拍攝的宣導短片中，作為瀕危的野生[[犀牛|犀牛]]的象徵<ref>{{cite web | url = https://wildaid.org/extinction-reversible-movies-wildaid-partners-jurassic-world-save-rhinos/ | title = Extinction is Only Reversible in Movies: WildAid Partners with Jurassic World to Save Rhinos | author = WildAid | date = 2018-06-26 | access-date = 2019-07-21 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190306102330/https://wildaid.org/extinction-reversible-movies-wildaid-partners-jurassic-world-save-rhinos/ | archive-date = 2019-03-06 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。而作為侏羅紀世界系列中登場的生物，中國角龍也在相關[[電子遊戲|電子遊戲]]《[[侏羅紀世界：進化|侏羅紀世界：進化]]》中以免費[[可下載內容|可下載內容]]的形式出現<ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.gamerevolution.com/guides/432309-jurassic-world-evolution-dlc | title = Jurassic World Evolution DLC: What’s in the New Expansion? | author = Capel, Chris | publisher = [[Game_Revolution|Game Revolution]] | date = 2018-11-08 | access-date = 2019-07-20 | archive-date = 2022-01-23 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220123053359/https://www.gamerevolution.com/guides/432309-jurassic-world-evolution-dlc }}</ref>。

